Package: SMCcalibration
Version: 2.1.1.9999
Date: 2015-09-07
Title: Calibration tool for soil moisture sensors
Author: Johannes Brenner <Johannes.Brenner@eurac.com>
Maintainer: Johannes Brenner <Johannes.Brenner@eurac.com>
Description: Calibrates soil moisture sensors using volumetric
    water content (VWC) measured in-situ by soil moisture sensors and retrieved 
    from soil samples. Includes interactive shiny app for data upload and 
    subseting, estimation of linear models (OLS and robust MM-type estimator), 
    visualisation of data and model estimate.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
License: LGPL (>= 2)
LazyData: No
LazyLoad: No
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    shiny,
    ggplot2,
    Cairo, 
    robustbase,
    leaflet,
    leaflet.extras, 
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    devtools
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
